  "rule_text": "In the 'FLIP THE SCRIPT' display lockup, the word 'THE' is flipped upside down; 'ON IBS-C' is set in Avenir Light (campaign.lockup.on_ibsc.weight) at 50% opacity (campaign.lockup.on_ibsc.opacity), with the hyphen replaced by the brand swoosh at 100% opacity (campaign.lockup.swoosh). See \u00a72.6.",
